<font class="pn-normal">It's been a long time since I've posted any News Articles.  Now I'm finding more time on my hands, despite having my computer and everything else lost by the movers.  I may not have <a href="http://www.EverQuest.com/" title="EverQuest™" target="_blank">EQ</a>, but at least I can get on VAZAELLE.NET!  =)<br />
<br />
Here are some of the things I've been working on behind the scenes of <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="Knights of the Green Mist" target="_blank">KGM</a> and <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">NATO</a> in the past couple weeks...</font><br>
