<td><font class="pn-title"><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=4&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">New Poll</a></font><br>
<font class="pn-normal">Please note that there is a new Poll to vote on.  This poll is in regards to Epic mondays, and when the best time really is for everyone so we can get the highest turnouts from all <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">NATO</a> guilds.  Each days is for Evenings, with the exception of Saturday and Sunday, where there is an option for AM or PM....please double-check your selection before hitting the &quot;Vote&quot; button.   Once the day of the week is selected, I will set a Poll for the Time of day.  This should be done in about 2 weeks, to allow everyone plenty of time to log in and cast their vote.<br />
<br />
- X<br />
</font><br>
<font class="pn-sub">Published Nov 09, 2002 - 09:49 PM</font>
